- v=-1: sum=0; sum-T=0, freq has 0 with count 1 → count=1; freq={0:2,1:1}
- v=1: sum=1; sum-T=1, freq has 1 with count 1 → count=2; freq={0:2,1:2}
- v=-1: sum=0; sum-T=0, freq has 0 with count 2 → count=4; freq={0:3,1:2}

